Rectify it...to charge  capacitor with a parallel blead resistor, lamp or anything else to discharge capacitor few seconds after saw turn off.

Comparator to output high when capacitor above a trigger voltage. Fet, relay... what ever kind of switch good for load to trigger on by saw being turned on.
